casebody.data:
SUPREME COURT. Bonesteel, appellant, agt. Lynde and others, respondents.

Monroe General Term,

September, 1853.

Welles, Johnson, and T. R. Strong, Justices.

The decision at special term, in this case, as reported in the present volume, ante p. 226, was affirmed on appeal, at the present term, and for the reasons stated by the justice at the special term.
